Since 2020 I had the idea of building my first blog. I experimente with different technologies, but I never finished it. I went upon several CMS, like WordPress, Strapi and others, but I never liked the complexity of them. I wanted to build a simple blog, where I can write my posts in Markdown and have a nice layout my own way.

## My main requirements

As of requirements, I wanted to have a simple blog with the following features:

- Write posts in Markdown
- Use SvelteKit for the frontend
- Lack of a complex CMS/Backend
- Easy to deploy and maintain
- Support for code blocks and syntax highlighting
- Support for images and Mermaid diagrams

